data.description: Welcome to modern living in this 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home, built in 2020. Spanning 2,208 sq ft and set on a 1-acre lot, fully fenced around the house, on a dead-end street, this residence features a 5th room, as an office or additional living space, enhancing its smart and spacious design. Upstairs, there are 2 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, while downstairs, there are 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  Ground Floor Features:  -The primary suite and bathroom, walk-in closet, and an additional closet for extra storage.  -Two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom.  -The ground floor boasts a separate entrance, enhancing privacy and offering possibilities for multi-generational living or rental options.  -A covered lanai provides a serene outdoor space.  -A large living room for family gatherings and entertainment.  -Convenient laundry room.  Upper Floor Layout:  -An enclosed lanai, perfect for both relaxation and dining, seamlessly connects to the main living area.  -Open-concept kitchen featuring sleek granite countertops and sturdy hardwood cabinets.  -The upper living room features vaulted T&G Pine ceilings and recessed lighting, creating an airy and inviting ambiance.  -A half bathroom is conveniently located off the dining area, linking the kitchen and living room.  -An additional full bathroom is positioned between the primary bedroom, which includes a walk-in closet, and the flex room, office, or additional living space.  This home in Hawaiian Paradise Park provides a practical and flexible living space, suitable for a variety of needs and lifestyles.
